 "name": "RPlog_Parley_For_Brandis_-_Part_2",
 "title": "Parley for Brandis (Part 2)",
 "summary": "Aboard the Imperial flagship at Selene, the parley for the captured Jedi Brandis Finian gives way to action as Luke Skywalker's team -- Kyrin Sh'vani, Johanna, and Ai'kani -- moves to extract Brandis from the heart of the Empire. Working in Force-harmony, the Jedi navigate the ship's defenses and the looming presence of Grand Admiral Kreldin and his Sith Master. The delegation presses deeper into the vessel toward Brandis, the negotiation collapsing into a daring rescue.",
